body_html:
You can find some usages in tests. The blog post is pretty old to the speed
of development of TF.

On Friday, September 16, 2016, Peter Waller notifications@github.com
wrote:

The blog post doesn't mention SessionRunHook, can you point me at an
example which uses it?

In particular, it's not clear how (before it was removed)
TensorFlowDNNAutoencoder maintained state between fit and transform, and
how to hook this up with SessionRunHook.
